original_title: on top and through one another ii
overview: In a continued state of chaos and common lines - maybe lonelier, even looking more closely through the clearness: "I think you're looking for new dreams" they said. Unknowingly, we've found new spaces, filled with stories and thoughts, new sounds and trees, new times, all travelling - always and forever - on top and through one another.
title: on top and through one another ii
